st_flatStats0.concerningText: Passive: Warwick senses all enemy  champions on the map who are damaged below  50% of their maximum health by an allied source, marking them with Blood Hunt until they regenerate above the threshold again. He sees trails leading toward them and gains  bonus movement speed while following the path. This bonus is lost for 0.5 seconds upon entering combat with an enemy champion, but will build up again over the next 3.5 seconds.
